Package: fastmlm
Title: Fast Multilevel Model Estimation
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("First", "Last", email = "first.last@example.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Fast estimation of multilevel (mixed-effects) linear models using
    optimised C++ computational backends with direct BLAS linkage, automatic
    differentiation for exact gradients, and optional GPU acceleration. Provides
    a drop-in interface compatible with lme4 formula syntax while achieving
    significant speedups through sparse Cholesky factorisation with pattern
    reuse, L-BFGS-B optimisation, and Krylov subspace methods for crossed
    random effects.
